{"tid":2291841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英媒：英國將增軍費鞏固區內影響力 建網絡部隊及太空司令部","createTime":"2020-11-19T05:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T05:45:22.000Z","uid":21470,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d008629de71274c8c99f5f1a503e4342763e0a78","tid":2291841,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T05:20:53.000Z","msg":"約翰遜將宣布冷戰以來英國最大軍事投資<br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒報道，首相約翰遜將會宣布，未來4年會大幅增加165億英鎊的軍事開支，是冷戰結束以來，英國最大的軍事投資。約翰遜今日將在國會演說，提出在疫情期間宣布這個決定，是因為英國以防衛為優先事項，認為當前國際環境比冷戰以來任何時候嚴峻及競爭激烈，希望以尖端軍事及網絡能力作為後盾，令脫歐後的英國得以在全球合作與自由貿易的新時代，扮演領導者角色。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，英國增加軍事預算，將鞏固英國作為歐洲最大及北約第2大防衛支出者的地位，約翰遜亦會宣布成立國家網絡部隊，負責人工智能的新機構，亦會成立新的太空司令部，爭取在2022年具備發射英國第一枚火箭的能力。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2366933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2366933&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5lLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=3efeab9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2366933</a>"},{"pid":"75c6a2165710d7ee839b67a4a45ab415bc739f5d","tid":2291841,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T05:21:58.000Z","msg":"拎百幾億去奶共好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ca2f083b08ec8dd465afe8e3a79dc39f74e889","tid":2291841,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T05:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7229e3ebff42728667fe11ca1c18047bbb27cda6","tid":2291841,"uid":362121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T05:41:22.000Z","msg":"中完武肺醒哂<br />\n<br />\n日出帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aadc07ecc5a1d4a4c374f5d954da2d665d340bc6","tid":2291841,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T05:45:22.000Z","msg":